{
  "stem": "27748.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, perhaps, they were doing us a favor by not forcing us to confront-- but, of course, they didn't-- nobody knew that there were death programs underway.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But simply the issue of what was going on with our parents, we couldn't-- we didn't talk about at Bunce Court.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was a community, of a sense, people who were going through the same things that were-- there there were vast areas of silence.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What were you preparing yourself, or what were they preparing you for, when you would graduate Bunce Court?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, first of all, I should mention the graduation time was when we were about 15.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was less than American high schools.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some people who were doing very well were encouraged to stay another two years to go for the higher school certificate, or the matriculation to the universities.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was not encouraged, because I did so badly in the mock exam.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some did better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I didn't come out as-- with a sense of a rosy future, except possibly doing something with my hands.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was another influence during that time that worked in the other direction on me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That is in London there was-- it seems that much of my life is made up of-- strong women seem to enter my life, my mother, [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anna Essinger. ?] There was another strong woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Her name was Herta Karger, K-A-R-G-E-R.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was a woman, again German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She had been-- she was born in Poland, and moved to Germany in the early 1900s.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was from a very wealthy family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she married a man who had become independently very successful in life in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And lo and behold, he died very young.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
